{"tid":2173962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急]聲援襲擊美領職員既施襲者","createTime":"2020-08-25T14:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T22:45:13.000Z","uid":134683,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"847c92f62c79a97f6f237a804aa5ea2bf3bd070f","tid":2173962,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"【22:05】據知施襲男子晚上9時左右於屯門被捕，犯案疑受毒品影響。<br />\n<br />\n【19:45】《蘋果》向美國駐港澳總領事館查詢，發言人其後回覆，證實一名職員被不知名人士襲擊，職員受傷但無性命危險，基於私隱考慮不能提供遇襲職員更多資料。領事館正就事件與香港警方保持緊密溝通，目前未能推測行兇者動機。<br />\n<br />\n一名美國駐港澳總領事館職員，下午4時許在中環花園道館址一帶，被一名本地男子揮拳襲擊。該名職員頭部受創流血，需要送瑪麗醫院治理，至於施襲男子事後則逃之夭夭，未知是否已被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n目前警方仍在場了解事件，案件暫列襲擊導致他人身體遭受實際傷害，暫時未知施襲男子是否被捕，其身份及犯案動機仍待調查。"},{"pid":"45098185a8003ef0cc9faa9ff3e6f896922b3cdd","tid":2173962,"uid":134683,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"明既自然會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8efbeb87e7b6b3ed6db6ae96a98d39938033a24","tid":2173962,"uid":134683,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"唔關毒品事<br />\n愛國無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925d3faef631741770463c3444dd32b118202f19","tid":2173962,"uid":15605,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"搵個道友認咗佢"},{"pid":"a67b8b8009c68c55fd8a0f6b98aaf296dcf60f63","tid":2173962,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1db15cc9aefaf7f26e534f2e373cfd0d781104","tid":2173962,"uid":34869,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"愛國咪就係效果最大既毒品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c3ea86a523017a8cee20eb813b6b0490bb6f62","tid":2173962,"uid":193077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"扶清滅洋"},{"pid":"65189054b25e5966d9e29b2618e78d972683fef2","tid":2173962,"uid":156913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"72c3ea86a523017a8cee20eb813b6b0490bb6f62","tid":2173962,"uid":193077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"扶清滅洋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"扶共滅洋"},{"pid":"08e334e346b1c68024051f8507b718c29de78b1e","tid":2173962,"uid":222970,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:37:35.000Z","msg":"大家唔好淨係喺連登圍爐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲幫手去藍絲group分化<br />\n<br />\n依家警察拉咗反美藍絲，藍絲一直都支持警察，估唔到而家警察忘恩負義，香港警察已經向美國低頭，真係對香港警察好失望！<br />\n<br />\n我之前仲喺隧道幫手拆詆毁香港警察嘅連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n搞到我仲比幾個黑暴打到流血<br />\n<br />\n估唔到香港警察而家竟然要保護美國人<br />\n<br />\n以後再有支持警察嘅活動我都唔會再參加！"},{"pid":"6375ba70e0131f49fdd85f71c7bc50fcc35f00ac","tid":2173962,"uid":103050,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"好心黑警換左個編劇佢啦<br />\n成撚日作埋d垃圾<br />\n小學生都呃唔到"},{"pid":"574d9743f74336f33212f065732a0495cc55e5c0","tid":2173962,"uid":78295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"點可能咁巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca192e682aff6b29e356aab91b05435c3690c0ee","tid":2173962,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"925d3faef631741770463c3444dd32b118202f19","tid":2173962,"uid":15605,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"搵個道友認咗佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"咩道友<br />\n愛國人士黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16371dae285eef22b3801396e8b56